SELECT 900015, 'Advanced Kettlebell Windmill', mg.id, 'kettlebell', NULL, '["Clean and press a kettlebell overhead with one arm.","Keeping the kettlebell locked out at all times, push your butt out in the direction of the locked out kettlebell. Keep the non-working arm behind your back and turn your feet out at a forty-five degree angle from the arm with the kettlebell.","Lower yourself as far as possible.","Pause for a second and reverse the motion back to the starting position."]', false, NULL
